{
  "stem": "27767.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they must know what's happened, and to be able to-- to-- if ever could happen something like this, to able to fight it, to fight against it, because I was thinking, if we knew something like this happened, if they would have announce on the radio, look, they're killing Jews, and they knew.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew-- the newspaper, the government in America knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Britain, they knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They knew they are killing Jews, and they are killing-- mass killings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they could have bombed the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They could have bomb the railroads.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They could have-- they could have slowed down the killings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nothing was done.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if we knew what's happening, we wouldn't have gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They would have kill us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They would have kill a lot of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But maybe some more would have escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it's very-- I decided it's very important to tell the new generation, to tell the children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's why I was talking about this in-- in several places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had-- I made a speech-- we have every year, a memorial in the New Montefiore Cemetery in Long Island.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "For the [INAUDIBLE] Baia-Mare area, [INAUDIBLE] Oradea-Mare, Jews, for the Holocaust survivors, and for the memorial for the Holocaust-- who were killed in the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We have a big memorial there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And every year, we-- some people, some survivors, one survivor makes a speech, and some children of survivors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I spoke there about three years ago, about the Holocaust, some of-- you know, they give you only 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So they have to do it concentrated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and they ask me-- we-- in the summer-- we have a bungalow in the summer and near Fishkill near Poughkeepsie.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there were over 50 families there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They asked me Tisha B'Av to speak about the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
